{"id": 1289, "genre": 1000, "title": "你见过哪些被滥用的定律？", "description": "世间一切事情，都可以用（畅销书上的）定律解释？（题图来自：Josh Holinaty）", "record_count": 8424, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161025143246s1vhRX45wdeBbigk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-26T17:00:14Z", "questions": [{"id": 1260, "title": "你见过哪些被滥用的定律？", "content": "你见过哪些被滥用的定律？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 127300, "content": "遇到任何不顺心的事情，都用“墨菲定律”解释", "image": "img/option/option/20161025151436VufPrcGFhsEzSY1K.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 127302, "content": "动不动就把自己的缺点比作“木桶的短板”", "image": "img/option/option/20161025151247dYM4UamCKwjhcJqv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 127310, "content": "看腻了新闻里的“蝴蝶效应”，所有因果关系都能套上这个帽子", "image": "img/option/option/20161025151538wQPHbaxlYOeis841.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 127315, "content": "用“羊群效应”“乌合之众”解释所有流行趋势和公共事件", "image": "img/option/option/20161025153200RBJqjsWnpyaOIVfF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 127316, "content": "没有遭遇困难，就叫“温水煮青蛙”效应", "image": "img/option/option/20161025153852u3KxoZYwtdzpIVNS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 127317, "content": "马太效应被用来解释所有得不到资源、失败的事情", "image": "img/option/option/20161025154327pwg8BemuIy3NFsqt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 127322, "content": "所有一连串的坏事都是因为“破窗效应”导致的", "image": "img/option/option/20161025160225EKXbZemy9Uh1q5Ld.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}